# Sprint 4 — packaging build artifacts (PyInstaller + Tauri sidecar)
# The sidecar binaries are produced by CI on tag push; we don't
# commit them. The build/ + dist/ globs above already cover
# PyInstaller output but be explicit about the staged sidecar dir.
tauri-app/src-tauri/binaries/
!tauri-app/src-tauri/binaries/.gitkeep
